QuestData.Title: Hungry Work
QuestData.Description: We must get Chief Telemancer Oculeth back on his feet as soon as possible.$B$BFind ancient mana, any way you can, and feed it to him.
QuestData.LogDescription: Use Ancient Mana to feed Chief Telemancer Oculeth.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, I am feeling much better. Thank you!$B$BNow let us get to work.
